name: Diplomats of the Time Tombs
description: Part of the community of divers searching for the grave of Akak Gagak, the Diplomats of the Time Tombs were involved in the initial conception of the Thespin Skytram. Now almost finished uncovering the details about chronomancers and their magics from aeons past, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
